'''Mariza Corrêa''' (1 December 1945 – 27 December 2016) was a Brazilian [[anthropologist]]<ref>{{cite book|title = História da antropologia no Brasil (1930–1960): testemunhos|url = https://www.worldcat.org/title/historia-da-antropologia-no-brasil-1930-1960-testemunhos/oclc/18015916|publisher = Editora da Universidade Estadual de Campinas|date = 1987|location = São Paulo, Brasil|isbn = 8585068426|language = Portuguese|first = Mariza|last = Corrêa|first2 = Emílio|last2 = Willems|first3 = Donald|last3 = Pierson}}</ref> and [[Sociology|sociologist]]. She was professor at the Department of Anthropology of the [[University of Campinas|State University of Campinas]] (Unicamp).<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariza Corrêa {{!}} Núcleo de Estudos de Gênero |url=http://www.pagu.unicamp.br/node/24 |date=2013-03-13 |accessdate=2015-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313104134/http://www.pagu.unicamp.br/node/24 |archivedate=March 13, 2013 }}</ref>
Trained in journalism in the [[Universidade Federal do Rio Grande do Sul|Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul]] (1969), she started to study social sciences in the State University of Campinas where she graduated in 1975. She earned in 1982 her PhD in Political Sciences at the [[University of São Paulo]] with a thesis on [[Raimundo Nina Rodrigues]].<ref>{{cite journal|title = Raimundo Nina Rodrigues: an avant la lettre anthropologist|url = http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract&pid=S0104-59702001000400015&lng=en&nrm=iso&tlng=pt|journal = História, Ciências, Saúde-Manguinhos|issn = 0104-5970|pages = 761–766|volume = 8|issue = 3|doi = 10.1590/S0104-59702001000400015|first = Carlos Henrique Assunção|last = Paiva|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101220072916/http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract|archivedate = 2010-12-20|df = }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title = As ilusões da liberdade: a Escola Nina Rodrigues e a antropologia no Brasil|url = https://www.worldcat.org/title/ilusoes-da-liberdade-a-escola-nina-rodrigues-e-a-antropologia-no-brasil/oclc/42717405|publisher = Instituto Franciscano de Antropologia, Centro de Documentação e Apoio à Pesquisa em História da Educação, Universidade São Francisco|date = 1998|location = Bragança Paulista, Brazil|isbn = 8586965014|language = Portuguese|first = Mariza|last = Corrêa}}</ref>
Between 1996 and 1998, she was president of the Associação Brasileira de Antropologia.<ref>{{cite web|title = Conselhos|url = http://www.portal.abant.org.br/index.php/institucional/conselhos|website = Associação Brasileira de Antropologia|accessdate = 2015-11-10}}</ref>
